  <bioghist id="aspace_84acf2db77199d607fc461f6452bcfc9">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Preacher in Elmira, New York, and New York National Guard chaplain.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_4a8976445863ace967d9282ef4492501">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Sermons, notes, reviews, an article about Jabberwocks,F. Kennicutt Beecher's phrenological chart, letter from "Sam'l L. Clemens" [not an original], certificate of chaplaincy; also, letters from Lyman Beecher containing advice and news on family matters, and from H. W. Beecher and M. A. Rockwood.</p>  </scopecontent>
